Title: Trend CSB/PT160/3PK CraftPro Panel Trim Saw Blade 160 x 20mm x 48T (Pack 3) TREPT1603P
Description:
1 x Pack of 3 Trend CraftPro CSB/PT16048 Plunge Saw Blades 160 x 20mm x 48T

The Trend CraftPro Plunge Saw Blade is designed to provide a professional finish in particle board, plywood, MDF and hardboard. It has a high-grade, hardened and tempered, alloy steel plate body that has been precision ground to maintain flatness. Silver brazed to ensure tips are securely bonded to body. With a reamed bore to ensure a precise spindle fit.

Laser etched on reverse to European standard EN 847-1/2.
